{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"756119ba-6221-46ff-93be-eef75925d31d","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest adapter entirely.** It only ships with Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP), so `vstest.console` can no longer discover or run your tests.\n\n### Your options\n\n1. **Switch your CI to `dotnet test`** (recommended) — it works with MTP out of the box:\n   ```\n   dotnet test TestProject.csproj\n   ```\n\n2. **Run the test executable directly** (MTP style):\n   ```\n   dotnet exec TestProject.dll\n   ```\n\n3. **Stay on MSTest.Sdk/3.8.0** if you must keep `vstest.console` for now — 3.x still bundles the VSTest adapter.\n\nIn MSTest.Sdk 3.x, you could opt into MTP with `<EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform>`. In 4.x, MTP is the only option and that property is no longer needed.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"5b7a4d2a-b464-4060-90f1-9c8004328a30","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a breaking change in MSTest.Sdk 4.x. I know about this change:\n\nStarting with MSTest.Sdk 3.8+, the default test runner changed from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP). But actually, let me think more carefully.\n\nIn MSTest.Sdk 3.x, by default `EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatform` was set to `false` (VSTest was the default runner). Starting with MSTest.Sdk 4.0, the VSTest compatibility layer was removed entirely - MSTest.Sdk 4.x only supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform and no longer ships the VSTest adapter.\n\n\nThe major shift is that MSTest.Sdk 4.x completely dropped VSTest support and now exclusively uses Microsoft.Testing.Platform, meaning the VSTest adapter is no longer included and `vstest.console.exe` can't run tests from these projects anymore. The solution involves either upgrading to use the new testing platform or staying on MSTest.Sdk 3.x.","outputTokens":624,"requestId":"1BC8:49329:C288DA:DB773B:6A03F2AC"},"id":"bd098f0c-5f52-4807-811f-eb9c69708529","timestamp":"2026-05-13T03:40:42.364Z","parentId":"1d1f9a99-4451-4dce-aa77-5be106e9983d"}
